# Generated caches/build outputs
**/.cache/
**/.zig-cache/
**/zig-out/
**/build-output/

# Runtime pid/socket/log artifacts
**/.httpd.pid
**/.ttyd.pid
**/.am.dtach
**/.am.lock
**/*.pid
**/*.log

# Local backup/snapshot system artifacts
**/vinvin/
**/.snap.*/
**/*.patch.gz

# Large model/binary payloads not suitable for standard git push
**/*.gguf
**/*.tar
**/*.tar.xz
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.zip

